<td class="mbox-text" style="">The <b><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Neutral_point_of_view" title="Wikipedia:Neutral point of view">neutrality</a> of this article is <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:NPOV_dispute" title="Wikipedia:NPOV dispute">disputed</a></b>. Please see the discussion on the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Eckankar" title="Talk:Eckankar">talk page</a>. Please do not remove this message until the <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:NPOVD#What_is_an_NPOV_dispute.3F" title="Wikipedia:NPOVD" class="mw-redirect">dispute is resolved.</a> <small><i>(September 2008)</i></small></td>
